Sheets of paper, papyrus, vellum, cloth and even birch bark cover this notice board, often in layers several pages deep, announcing, advertising, offering or seeking all sorts of events, meetings or services, most clearly spelled out but others only hinted at. Many of the notices bear scribbled comments, sometimes directed to the bona fides or moral qualities of the original poster and occasionally of dubious relevance (or even sanity).
